1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
ظآزI found a faint light
in the fading duskظآز

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
ظآزAnd met your steady gazeظآز

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
ظآزOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk onظآز

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
ظآزLonging finds no place to restظآز

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
ظآزThrough drifting wind and rainظآز

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
ظآزYou are the prayer within my handsظآز

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
ظآزA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knowsظآز

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
ظآزWe made a promise long agoظآز

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
ظآزFor all our days to comeظآز

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
ظآزYou are the fate I cannot outrunظآز

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
ظآزHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?ظآز

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
ظآزHolding you closeظآز

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
ظآزWould that be enough?ظآز

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,779
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,780 --> 00:01:01,499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,670
=Episode 23=

17
00:01:18,139 --> 00:01:22,060
My son is the true Emperor.

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:25,179
In this world,

19
00:01:25,940 --> 00:01:28,500
no one can compare to you.

20
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:41,060
It's all gone.

21
00:01:44,139 --> 00:01:47,780
I have suffered so much.

22
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:52,659
Your Highness,

23
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,220
what suffering do you speak of?

24
00:01:55,699 --> 00:01:57,700
Those female performers you harmed

25
00:01:57,859 --> 00:01:59,860
and the Duchess you murdered

26
00:01:59,940 --> 00:02:02,500
are the ones who truly suffered.

27
00:02:03,779 --> 00:02:05,620
What did I do wrong?

28
00:02:06,740 --> 00:02:07,936
My son, King Gong,

29
00:02:07,937 --> 00:02:11,157
was the Emperor's most favored prince.

30
00:02:11,379 --> 00:02:13,819
Fourth Prince's mother died early,

31
00:02:13,939 --> 00:02:16,659
so the Retired Emperor let me adopt him.

32
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:19,979
He even sent
some maidservants to serve us.

33
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,460
My son

34
00:02:21,525 --> 00:02:23,819
just couldn't resist the temptation.

35
00:02:24,212 --> 00:02:26,518
Fourth Prince sure knew how to act.

36
00:02:26,779 --> 00:02:29,659
He treated those maidservants
with such respect.

37
00:02:30,962 --> 00:02:33,659
That's how he managed
to steal the throne.

38
00:02:35,912 --> 00:02:38,392
I will never accept this!

39
00:02:39,379 --> 00:02:42,020
It was clearly your son
who raped a maidservant first.

40
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:44,699
She took her revenge, leaving him
crippled and losing the throne.

41
00:02:44,939 --> 00:02:47,699
Yet you blame everything on women.

42
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:50,060
You are beyond saving.

43
00:03:01,339 --> 00:03:04,139
Do you have any idea
what life is like in the harem?

44
00:03:05,379 --> 00:03:07,139
Favored in the morning,

45
00:03:08,059 --> 00:03:10,500
sentenced to death by evening.

46
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,379
There wasn't a single moment

47
00:03:12,819 --> 00:03:15,740
when I lived for myself.

48
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:18,419
My son

49
00:03:19,379 --> 00:03:22,620
was the only hope of my life.

50
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:25,218
That's why I had to establish
the Shengtang Guild

51
00:03:25,219 --> 00:03:27,539
to give my son a second chance

52
00:03:28,219 --> 00:03:29,939
and to make those lowly women

53
00:03:30,099 --> 00:03:32,900
the stepping stones for my son's path.

54
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:41,419
As a woman yourself,

55
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:45,220
you know well the hardships
and struggles women face.

56
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,498
Yet you care only
for your husband and son,

57
00:03:47,499 --> 00:03:49,419
worshipping them like gods.

58
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:51,378
Then, you turn around and inflict

59
00:03:51,379 --> 00:03:53,379
all that suffering onto other women.

60
00:03:53,779 --> 00:03:54,780
You

61
00:03:55,659 --> 00:03:57,098
are far more pathetic and hateful

62
00:03:57,099 --> 00:03:58,939
than that darn son of yours.

63
00:03:59,779 --> 00:04:01,539
Be a good boy.

64
00:04:03,580 --> 00:04:05,580
- Be a good boy.
- But I suppose this is for the best.

65
00:04:08,062 --> 00:04:10,382
You will never have the chance
to see him again.

66
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:16,139
My son is the true
Emperor of this world.

67
00:04:28,859 --> 00:04:30,499
In the next life,

68
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:34,419
let's be mother and son again.

69
00:04:55,979 --> 00:04:57,619
It's finally over.

70
00:04:57,779 --> 00:04:58,739
Yes.

71
00:04:59,179 --> 00:05:00,380
The times have changed.

72
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:02,340
Everything is a new beginning.

73
00:05:17,580 --> 00:05:20,379
(Gu Chengye possessed
extraordinary strategy,)

74
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:22,139
(unmatched bravery,)

75
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:24,098
(and illustrious military achievements.)

76
00:05:24,099 --> 00:05:27,858
(To honor the remarkable
contributions of these two,)

77
00:05:27,859 --> 00:05:31,218
(Song Zhiyun is removed
from the lower class)

78
00:05:31,219 --> 00:05:34,011
(and titled as a Noble Lady.)

79
00:05:34,012 --> 00:05:37,411
(Furthermore, seeing their deep
devotion to each other,)

80
00:05:37,412 --> 00:05:39,974
(I hereby bestow
this marriage upon them.)

81
00:05:39,975 --> 00:05:43,024
(May you live in harmony
for a hundred years,)

82
00:05:43,025 --> 00:05:47,345
(forever of one heart.
By Imperial Decree.)

83
00:05:47,587 --> 00:05:50,882
ظآزA sharp arrow pierces through memoryظآز

84
00:05:51,787 --> 00:05:52,787
My wife,

85
00:05:54,739 --> 00:05:56,179
it's getting late.

86
00:05:56,339 --> 00:05:57,499
Should we

87
00:05:58,539 --> 00:06:00,179
retire for the night?

88
00:06:01,775 --> 00:06:04,298
ظآزAfter endless sorrow enduredظآز

89
00:06:04,299 --> 00:06:05,419
Wait a moment.

90
00:06:06,179 --> 00:06:08,299
I still have something
very important to do.

91
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:18,900
As expected of
the Imperial Guard Commander.

92
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:21,659
This dowry is incredibly generous.

93
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:24,380
Look at all this gold.

94
00:06:28,380 --> 00:06:30,260
The price of gold
must be skyrocketing now.

95
00:06:30,659 --> 00:06:32,659
I wonder how much this would sell for.

96
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:35,178
When I die, wherever I'm buried,
it must be recorded in the family annals.

97
00:06:35,179 --> 00:06:36,680
I don't want anyone
to lose track of it later.

98
00:06:38,339 --> 00:06:39,900
What are you talking about?

99
00:06:41,339 --> 00:06:42,780
Nothing.

100
00:06:43,179 --> 00:06:44,459
This money...

101
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:46,940
Half for you, and half for me.

102
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:50,739
It's all yours.
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

103
00:06:57,837 --> 00:06:59,961
ظآزNight rain falls before the courtyardظآز

104
00:06:59,962 --> 00:07:01,874
ظآزIlluminating the partings
of the mortal worldظآز

105
00:07:01,875 --> 00:07:02,995
Wait.

106
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,859
I have more to say.

107
00:07:05,859 --> 00:07:06,820
Gu Chengye,

108
00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:08,820
I am not like
those other women out there.

109
00:07:08,859 --> 00:07:10,820
I cannot accept you
having multiple wives.

110
00:07:11,237 --> 00:07:13,374
For the rest of your life,
you can only have me.

111
00:07:13,375 --> 00:07:15,220
And you absolutely
cannot go fooling around.

112
00:07:15,232 --> 00:07:18,936
ظآزLonging spreads like inkظآز

113
00:07:18,937 --> 00:07:23,338
ظآزBeaded curtains divide love
and hate at either endظآز

114
00:07:23,339 --> 00:07:26,059
My heart is steadfast and will not turn.

115
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:29,579
I wish to have one person
to grow old with.

116
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:32,365
ظآزLove is a word too hard to severظآز

117
00:07:33,162 --> 00:07:36,998
ظآزPast ties fade like a dream gone coldظآز

118
00:07:36,999 --> 00:07:39,671
ظآزIn giving all, we found our only joyظآز

119
00:07:39,672 --> 00:07:43,311
ظآزThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossomsظآز

120
00:07:43,312 --> 00:07:46,886
ظآزOne night of snow
fell wild and restlessظآز

121
00:07:46,887 --> 00:07:53,811
ظآزEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regretظآز

122
00:07:53,812 --> 00:07:57,311
ظآزWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewellظآز

123
00:07:57,312 --> 00:08:01,391
ظآزNo more longing will enter my dreamsظآز

124
00:08:01,392 --> 00:08:07,724
ظآزWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with youظآز

125
00:08:07,725 --> 00:08:10,632
(Double Happiness)

126
00:08:28,299 --> 00:08:29,419
Could it be

127
00:08:32,179 --> 00:08:33,979
that all of this was just a dream?

128
00:08:45,579 --> 00:08:46,899
(Liu Ruyan)

129
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:49,460
(The top courtesan queen
of Huanyue House.)

130
00:08:49,812 --> 00:08:52,284
(Exquisite in the art
of makeup and styling.)

131
00:08:52,579 --> 00:08:54,899
(She later married Gu Chengye,
son of the Duke.)

132
00:08:55,579 --> 00:08:58,940
(The two were perfectly matched
and in harmony.)

133
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:02,379
(They spent a happy
and fulfilling life together.)

134
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:43,160
ظآزEven if I drift
within a darkened whirlظآز

135
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:47,011
ظآزKindred souls
meet the light and become oneظآز

136
00:09:47,012 --> 00:09:54,849
ظآزSo many chapters,
every wound rememberedظآز

137
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:58,736
ظآزBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remainظآز

138
00:09:58,737 --> 00:10:02,007
ظآزThe night runs deep like watching eyesظآز

139
00:10:02,362 --> 00:10:04,199
ظآزWave after wave of sorrowظآز

140
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:07,736
ظآزIn exchange, no one will ever knowظآز

141
00:10:07,737 --> 00:10:10,070
ظآزI will waitظآز

142
00:10:11,687 --> 00:10:14,136
ظآزLonging finds no place to restظآز

143
00:10:14,137 --> 00:10:16,249
ظآزThrough drifting wind and rainظآز

144
00:10:16,250 --> 00:10:18,270
ظآزYou are the prayer within my handsظآز
